nard lanigan jr began his career as a member of a “big ” firm from that our practice was founded on the principles built through extensive public company experience and national accounting firm acumen  together they created a vision to solve client problems through cost effective planning and strategies in the  years since inception lanigan has grown into a fullservice regional accounting and consulting practice with locations in thomasville tallahassee and atlanta our firm has grown our practice from two members to over  professionals and support staff one of our greatest strengths is that we possess the size and expertise necessary to take on large and challenging projects in a wide variety of industries while maintaining a smallfirm feel such that we give each of our clients the personal touch and attention they deserve from their trusted advisor our principalsview biobernard lanigan jr cpachairmanview biofrank j mercer cpa cfpmanaging principalview bioc bradford jackson cpa cfaprincipalview biod mark fletcher cpa cfe cgmaprincipalview biog thomas harrison jr cpa cfpprincipalview biojohn w keillor cpa ciaprincipalview biomichael o sills jr cpa cfe cgmaprincipalour managersview infoglenn townsend cpa cgmasenior managerview infotom hoyt cpasenior managerview infodona reetzsenior managerview infojames s shaw iii cpa cgmasenior managerview infobryan millerit directorview infokeith eierhart cpatax managerview infoallison bassaccounting services managerview infoerik luoma cpaaudit managerview infowalker bridges cpatax managerview infodavid strange cpaaudit managerview infojanice stricklandoffice administratorview inforobert m milberg cpaof counsel lanigan bernard jr cpa in thomasville ga   chamberofcommercecom  sign up sign in contact us   search   near   home » georgia » thomasville » certified public accountants » lanigan bernard jr cpa lanigan bernard jr cpa  reviews  stars  based on  reviews  s hansell st thomasville georgia        print  save  directions about lan